story: Pwnky, a creature from the Black night of Inpinity Online, ventured through the digital realms with Green eyes eyes that sparkled with curiosity, a Mechanic body body that shimmered with the essence of creativity, and a Mechanic mouth  mouth that resonated with the voices of countless creators. On this journey, Pwnky's Comic ear ears fluttered in the electronic winds, and Long blue hair hair flowed like the rivers of code that shaped the landscape. Adorned with a Hat with leafs  hat crafted by the artisans of the net, Pwnky discovered the Jacket , a relic that could unlock new realms in this infinite universe.
description: a new Pwnkey with Black night, Green eyes, Mechanic body, Mechanic mouth , Comic ear, Long blue hair, Hat with leafs , Jacket
